clinical_trials.eligibility_criteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

1. Adults aged 18 years and older at the time of informed consent;
2. Diagnosis of rheumatic disease: rheumatoid arthritis (RA), psoriatic arthritis (PA) , ankylosing spondylitis (AS), systemic lupus erythematosus (SLE), juvenile idiopathic arthritis (JIA), spondyloarthritis, po

Inclusion Criteria:

* Signed Informed Consent;
* Male and female patients aged ≥55 years;
* Patients that according to the investigator's judgement will benefit from the proposed treatments (favourable benefit/risk profile)
* Menopause for women;(no menses for 12 months without an alternative medic
